@startuml GoFit_Sequence_WorkoutSession
title GoFit — Sequence: start → perform → complete workout session

actor User
participant "GoFit App\n(Expo / RN)" as App
participant "workoutService" as Svc
participant "Supabase JS" as SB
database "Postgres (RLS)" as DB

User -> App: Start workout from library / plan
App -> Svc: createWorkoutSession(userId, workout)
Svc -> SB: (optional) complete previous incomplete session
SB -> DB: UPDATE workout_sessions
Svc -> SB: INSERT workout_sessions
SB -> DB: INSERT
DB --> App: new session_id

loop Exercises and sets
  User -> App: Complete sets, rest, weights
  note right of App
    Mostly local state (timers, progress).
    Optional mid-session sync if implemented.
  end note
end

User -> App: Tap finish
App -> Svc: updateWorkoutSession(id, completed_at,\nduration, exercises_completed)
Svc -> SB: UPDATE workout_sessions
SB -> DB: UPDATE
DB --> App: saved session
App -> User: Workout summary screen

@enduml
